# Netlify redirect rules: the API sends WhatsApp/email links in the form
# /q/<token>, /i/<token>, /b/<token>, /pay/<token> (to keep links short and
# clean for clients). This site serves the same content as query-string
# static pages, so bridge one to the other here rather than changing the
# API's link-generation code.
/q/:token    /q.html?token=:token    200
/i/:token    /i.html?token=:token    200
/b/:token    /b.html?token=:token    200
/pay/:token  /pay.html?token=:token  200
/book/:slug  /book.html?slug=:slug  200
